<lb n="0353b07" ed="T"/>薩哩嚩<note place="inline">二合</note>怛他<note place="inline">引</note>誐多<note place="inline">二</note>嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>薩埵<note place="inline">引</note>提瑟
